@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_smrvci(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v0 = 0.66
    tmp = wp.cos(wp.exp(v1))
    v1 = tmp
    tmp = wp.cos(wp.abs(wp.exp(tmp + 0.54)))
    v1 = (wp.sin(wp.exp(v2 + 0.75)) - wp.abs(wp.cos(tmp + 0.20)))
    v2 = wp.abs((v1 / (v2 + 0.27 * v1 + 0.01)))
    data[tid] = v0
